com.github.rolecraftdev.profession

Class Profession

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.rolecraftdev.profession.Profession

  • public class Profession
extends Object
    Represents a profession that can be chosen by players. After a player has chosen a profession, events affecting that player will be handled according to the profession's ProfessionRules.
